a personalized video to him?

00:21:06.240 --> 00:21:08.202
And I said, well,
I'm in Singapore,

00:21:08.202 --> 00:21:09.910
and this is probably
the closest I'm ever

00:21:09.910 --> 00:21:10.951
going to be to Australia.

