Just to give you guys a quick
example, I think two days ago,

00:26:02.840 --> 00:26:05.160
I had a day off, and I
spontaneously decided to hop

00:26:05.160 --> 00:26:08.360
in the car and drive
to the Apple campus,

00:26:08.360 --> 00:26:11.080
